{
  "stem": "22511.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, they-- we had every [INAUDIBLE] and there was a special break to speak about the other world, what will happen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Saint Peter and he's there, and he will open the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they will pray to me, I will take them in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They believe in me that I will be a saint.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And really, I promise myself that if the war will be finished, and I will not find anyone from my family, I'm not going to marry.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I will become a nun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was my wish, because I wouldn't marry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I want to be a nun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Only-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I, I prayed every morning. 5:00 in the morning, we went to the [NON-ENGLISH], and we were doing our praying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then, every Sunday comes the priest, and we had to tell him what we'd done wrong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Even a dream, a bad dream, you had to tell, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I took it very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I studied to, to learn the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Catechism, the Bible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I loved it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I think it's good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was sorry why we couldn't do that and not to suffer so much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because the religion is the one bad thing what makes the problem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We all decent people, and we suffer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Even Jesus was Jewish, and now everybody prays to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we, the children of-- of his nation, suffering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is not right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, that's what-- what shall I tell you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only for me, it was easier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, I felt very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had an abscess under the arm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was really thinking I'm going to die.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
